### User Account Management API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:9090

### Variables for reusable values
@baseUrl = http://localhost:9090
@userId = 1
@testEmail = john.doe@example.com
@testPassword = password123

###
### 1. Create a new user account (Direct UserAccount object)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Charles DeFreese III",
  "userName": "cdefre3",
  "email": "cdefre3@wgu.edu",
  "password": "password123"
}

###
### 2. Get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Accept: application/json

###
### 3. Get user by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json

###
### 4. Update user email
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}/email?email=john.updated@example.com
Accept: application/json

###
### 5. Update user password
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}/password?password=newpassword123
Accept: application/json

###
### 6. Check user password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}/check-password?password={{testPassword}}
Accept: application/json

###
### 7. Check user email
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/5/check-email?email=cdefre3@wgu.edu
Accept: application/json

###
### 8. Delete user account (WARNING: This will delete the user)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/{{userId}}

